   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Responding to the Refugee Crisis in Europe</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">International Medical Corps is working to respond to the significant amount of need created by the current refugee crisis in Europe. UNHCR estimates that more than 1,000,000 refugees from Syria-as well as from other conflict-ridden places such as Iraq and Afghanistan-traversed the Mediterranean Sea to reach Europe in 2015. Since January 1, 2016,  more than 300,000 refugees and migrants from Syria, Afghanistan, Iraq and other nations have reached Europe by sea.</narrative>
  </description>
